Also you need to add Jar file "libandroid_tensorflow_inference_java.jar" under Library.

libandroid_tensorflow_inference_java.zip

libtensorflow_demo.zip
This is for x86_64 arch

body:
You need to change "libtensorflow_demo.so" file, the file attached in github code is not correct.
Add it under which ever arch you are using "arm64-v8a" or  'armeabi-v7a" or "x86" or "x86_64"
Also you need to add Jar file "libandroid_tensorflow_inference_java.jar" under Library.


[libandroid_tensorflow_inference_java.zip](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/files/1757273/libandroid_tensorflow_inference_java.zip)

[libtensorflow_demo.zip](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/files/1757275/libtensorflow_demo.zip)
This is for x86_64 arch
